Just to let you know, you are missing a whole 30min episode between what you have labeled as episodes 3 and 4. Your first file labeled "episodes 1 and 2" is really just ep 1 but an hour long so you are missing the real episode 3 from the torrent.

Good quality but it makes the story confusing and hard to follow without that episode.
